text: Plaffeien () is a municipality of the district of Sense in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. On 1 January 2017, the former municipalities of Oberschrot and Zumholz merged into the municipality of Plaffeien.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 10 January 2017 It is the third- largest municipality in the canton of Fribourg. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Sense District
